WEBVTT

1
00:00:14.624 --> 00:00:18.211
<b>DOBRODOŠLI
U CHERRY FALLS</b>


2
00:00:39.149 --> 00:00:41.526
Na mojoj planeti
žene su jalove.


3
00:00:43.946 --> 00:00:46.066
Potajno sam putovao

4
00:00:46.156 --> 00:00:49.450
dubinama svemira
poprimivši ljudski oblik


5
00:00:51.912 --> 00:00:54.539
kako bih upoznao Zemljanke

6
00:00:54.748 --> 00:00:57.250
i ponovo naselio
svoju pustu planetu.


7
00:01:00.546 --> 00:01:04.465
Želim da znaš
moje pravo ime. Xunobulax.


8
00:01:05.008 --> 00:01:06.425
Xunobulax?

9
00:01:09.513 --> 00:01:11.472
Moja rasa vodi ljubav
samo jednom.


10
00:01:13.392 --> 00:01:17.270
Ulažemo svu kosmičku
energiju u taj jedan čin,


11
00:01:19.523 --> 00:01:22.108
a onda, kao zemaljski
vodeni cvijet,


12
00:01:22.985 --> 00:01:25.653
umiremo i padamo
na tlo zadovoljni.


13
00:01:27.156 --> 00:01:29.949
Želim voditi ljubav
kako mi to radimo.


14
00:01:32.119 --> 00:01:33.744
Želim da to bude moj
posljednji čin.


15
00:01:34.371 --> 00:01:36.873
Nastaviš li,
bit će ti posljednji.


16
00:01:37.332 --> 00:01:39.417
Ne mogu se vratiti
neispunjene misije.


17
00:01:39.626 --> 00:01:41.294
Prestani!

18
00:01:47.718 --> 00:01:50.839
Želim da mi ti budeš prva.
- I ja.


19
00:01:50.929 --> 00:01:54.432
Dobro. Razumijem.
Molim te, Stacy.


20
00:02:17.581 --> 00:02:19.248
Koji je ovo vrag?

21
00:02:25.172 --> 00:02:26.505
Čekaj.

22
00:02:30.344 --> 00:02:33.387
Bene!
Dolazi ovamo!


23
00:02:34.848 --> 00:02:36.849
Mark, ti si unutra?

24
00:02:45.901 --> 00:02:47.235
Ovo nije smiješno!

25
00:02:49.238 --> 00:02:50.529
Koji vrag...

26
00:02:52.908 --> 00:02:54.325
Rode!

27
00:02:59.248 --> 00:03:00.623
Ne, Rode!

28
00:03:18.600 --> 00:03:19.976
Stacy...

29
00:03:23.150 --> 00:03:24.563
Stacy....

30
00:03:33.240 --> 00:03:34.573
Stacy!

31
00:03:40.622 --> 00:03:42.164
Stacy!

32
00:03:53.218 --> 00:03:54.593
Ne, Rode!

33
00:03:56.388 --> 00:03:57.596
Bože!

34
00:04:30.793 --> 00:04:35.316
<b>CHERRY FALLS</b>

35
00:04:35.406 --> 00:04:38.596
Trebala sam biti kući
prije 15 minuta.


36
00:04:38.889 --> 00:04:41.640
Klinci u šestom razredu
duže ostaju napolju.


37
00:04:48.940 --> 00:04:50.608
Ne, dušo, nemoj...

38
00:04:51.109 --> 00:04:52.401
Ne, ne, ne...

39
00:04:57.783 --> 00:04:59.367
Prestani.

40
00:05:00.577 --> 00:05:03.287
Ne bojiš se da ćeš
umrijeti nevina?


41
00:05:04.456 --> 00:05:06.957
To i globalno zagrijavanje.

42
00:05:14.216 --> 00:05:16.717
Moramo početi
izlaziti s drugima.


43
00:05:16.927 --> 00:05:18.010
Šta?

44
00:05:19.179 --> 00:05:20.137
Gle...

45
00:05:20.347 --> 00:05:21.842
Izlazimo već godinu dana,

46
00:05:21.932 --> 00:05:23.724
i mislim da ne ide.

47
00:05:23.934 --> 00:05:25.101
Uredu?

48
00:05:33.402 --> 00:05:35.444
Hej, gđo Marken.
- Zabavljate se?


49
00:05:35.654 --> 00:05:37.154
Zdravo, mama.

50
00:05:37.489 --> 00:05:40.741
Kenny, imaš cigaretu za mene?

51
00:05:42.494 --> 00:05:43.452
Naravno.

52
00:05:46.289 --> 00:05:49.500
Gospođo Marken,
pušenje škodi zdravlju.


53
00:05:52.879 --> 00:05:54.797
Ove su jake.

54
00:05:58.343 --> 00:05:59.718
Dužna sam ti uslugu.

55
00:06:00.720 --> 00:06:02.388
Moram ovdje pušiti.

56
00:06:02.931 --> 00:06:05.349
Brent ne voli
kada pušim u kući.


57
00:06:07.436 --> 00:06:11.439
To mi je zadnji grešni užitak.
- Je li tata još budan?


58
00:06:11.982 --> 00:06:15.359
Večeras smo kasno napolju, a?
- Kenny je baš krenuo kući.


59
00:06:16.820 --> 00:06:17.778
Šteta.

60
00:06:22.659 --> 00:06:25.072
Vazduh je čist.

61
00:06:25.162 --> 00:06:27.455
Požuri želiš li
izbjeći nevolje.


62
00:06:29.791 --> 00:06:30.958
Gđo Marken?

63
00:06:33.503 --> 00:06:36.255
Ostavili ste svjetla upaljena.
- Dobro zapažaš.


64
00:06:37.090 --> 00:06:39.049
Hvala. Laku noć.

65
00:06:39.426 --> 00:06:40.551
Hvala. Laku noć.

66
00:06:49.603 --> 00:06:51.812
Dakle, laku noć ili zbogom?

67
00:06:52.939 --> 00:06:54.231
Izaberi.

68
00:06:55.442 --> 00:06:57.651
Izaberi.
- Ti odluči.


69
00:07:08.246 --> 00:07:10.456
Nemoj... zalupiti vratima!

70
00:07:26.056 --> 00:07:28.265
Kao mišić.

71
00:08:02.884 --> 00:08:05.213
Znaš li koliko je sati?
- Prestrašio si me.


72
00:08:05.303 --> 00:08:07.304
Dvije sedmice nema izlazaka.

73
00:08:07.514 --> 00:08:09.515
I šestaši ostaju duže napolju.

74
00:08:09.724 --> 00:08:11.475
Oni nisu šerifova kći.

75
00:08:35.542 --> 00:08:37.126
Marken.

76
00:08:40.630 --> 00:08:43.215
Dolazim odmah.

77
00:09:00.317 --> 00:09:01.692
Tata.

78
00:09:31.514 --> 00:09:34.391
Sama si?
- Prva sam došla.


79
00:09:34.601 --> 00:09:37.019
Forenzičari i kriminalisti
stižu iz Richmonda.


80
00:09:37.228 --> 00:09:40.606
Žrtvin auto je sav krvav.

81
00:09:44.611 --> 00:09:48.614
Momak je ležao tu,
s licem u vodi...


82
00:09:48.907 --> 00:09:51.742
I milion ubodnih rana.
A djevojka...


83
00:09:53.203 --> 00:09:55.371
Pribijena je na stablo.

84
00:09:56.081 --> 00:09:59.333
Iz rana joj je isteklo
puno krvi, što znači...


85
00:09:59.542 --> 00:10:03.462
Da je još bila živa
dok se to događalo.


86
00:10:28.904 --> 00:10:29.858
Jody... čuj...

87
00:10:29.948 --> 00:10:32.324
Do ručka izlazi
posebno izdanje novina.


88
00:10:32.414 --> 00:10:35.494
Bit ću ti najbolji prijatelj ako
mi kažeš sve što znaš. Najbolji.


89
00:10:35.704 --> 00:10:38.330
Bit ćeš pomoćnik urednika
i upisati dobar faks


90
00:10:38.540 --> 00:10:40.457
pun frajera.
Šta kažeš?


91
00:10:41.084 --> 00:10:42.626
Nemoj šutjeti. Ne, ne, ne.

92
00:10:42.716 --> 00:10:45.879
Razgovaraj s tatom i
ispipaj stvar. Kontaš?


93
00:10:46.089 --> 00:10:48.507
Nemam pojma o čemu govoriš.

94
00:10:49.426 --> 00:10:51.301
Ne znaš za Roda i Stacy?

95
00:10:51.511 --> 00:10:54.596
Zapisuješ za
glupu rubriku tračeva?


96
00:10:55.098 --> 00:10:58.267
Prekinuli su? - Prekinuli?
Dobro jutro! Mrtvi su.


97
00:10:58.476 --> 00:11:00.644
Riknuli su,
stresli vrtlog zemaljski,


98
00:11:00.854 --> 00:11:02.563
odapeli i otišli Tvorcu.

99
00:11:04.315 --> 00:11:06.066
Kako si tako
neobaviještena?


100
00:11:06.276 --> 00:11:08.777
Cijela škola bruji o tome.

101
00:11:13.658 --> 00:11:14.569
Gle!

102
00:11:14.659 --> 00:11:18.162
Možda ipak ima nešto za
moju jadnu rubriku tračeva.


103
00:11:19.748 --> 00:11:21.665
Ja gledam oko sebe.

104
00:11:23.585 --> 00:11:26.253
G. Sisler,
došao je šerif Marken.


105
00:11:26.343 --> 00:11:27.713
Da ga uvedem?

106
00:11:27.922 --> 00:11:28.964
Da.

107
00:11:29.466 --> 00:11:30.800
Hvala, Diana.

108
00:11:36.931 --> 00:11:39.808
Dugo se nismo
vidjeli, Brente. - Tome.


109
00:11:47.358 --> 00:11:49.735
Ne moram ti govoriti
kakva je ludnica u školi.


110
00:11:50.153 --> 00:11:52.321
Otkazao sam nastavu

111
00:11:52.864 --> 00:11:55.783
i zamolio profesore da
utješe i savjetuju djecu.


112
00:11:55.992 --> 00:11:59.870
Znam da za to
postoje stručnjaci, ali...


113
00:12:00.204 --> 00:12:02.289
Činilo mi se bolje
da bude neko...


114
00:12:02.379 --> 00:12:05.459
Slušaj, Tome.
Morat ću u neke razrede


115
00:12:05.549 --> 00:12:07.169
i postaviti im pitanja.

116
00:12:08.588 --> 00:12:10.756
Najprije u njihovom.

117
00:12:11.466 --> 00:12:13.675
Znam, užasnuti ste

118
00:12:13.885 --> 00:12:16.804
bezumnim gubitkom prijatelja.

119
00:12:17.514 --> 00:12:19.306
Vjerovatno osjećate krivicu

120
00:12:19.516 --> 00:12:21.934
što niste bili bolji
prema njima dok su bili živi


121
00:12:22.024 --> 00:12:24.019
ili vas...
šta ja znam...


122
00:12:24.229 --> 00:12:27.481
progoni nešto ružno
što ste im rekli.


123
00:12:28.483 --> 00:12:31.902
U osmom razredu sam se
posvađala s Rodom.


124
00:12:32.111 --> 00:12:34.822
Rekla sam mu da se
goni i crkne!


125
00:12:41.454 --> 00:12:43.080
Smirite se.

126
00:12:45.291 --> 00:12:46.792
Uredu je, Heather.

127
00:12:49.420 --> 00:12:52.464
Možda će nam biti lakše
ako razgovaramo o njima


128
00:12:52.674 --> 00:12:54.091
i kako se osjećamo.

129
00:12:55.760 --> 00:12:58.637
Mark, bili ste prijatelji.
Želiš li šta reći?


130
00:13:00.431 --> 00:13:02.349
O, čovječe...

131
00:13:04.853 --> 00:13:06.979
Ne znam, ja sam...

132
00:13:08.106 --> 00:13:09.106
Hvala, Mark.

133
00:13:14.320 --> 00:13:15.904
A ti, Sandy?

134
00:13:17.991 --> 00:13:19.074
Sandy!

135
00:13:21.077 --> 00:13:21.910
Ja...

136
00:13:22.287 --> 00:13:24.746
Kad se dogodi ovako nešto...

137
00:13:25.582 --> 00:13:27.165
Nadam se da postoji raj.

138
00:13:27.834 --> 00:13:28.876
Jadno.

139
00:13:30.503 --> 00:13:31.795
Prestani, Cindy.

140
00:13:32.338 --> 00:13:33.755
U ovakvim trenucima

141
00:13:33.965 --> 00:13:35.549
moramo pomoći jedni drugima.

142
00:13:35.967 --> 00:13:38.051
Ja bih pomogla ubici

143
00:13:38.141 --> 00:13:40.179
da dođe do
električne stolice.


144
00:13:42.807 --> 00:13:44.224
Opravdana reakcija,

145
00:13:44.434 --> 00:13:47.936
ali sad to rade
smrtonosnom injekcijom.


146
00:13:48.855 --> 00:13:53.150
Bene, znam da ti drugačije
gledaš na ovu tragediju.


147
00:13:53.359 --> 00:13:54.359
Pa...

148
00:13:56.821 --> 00:13:58.030
Izvoli.

149
00:13:58.698 --> 00:14:01.986
Zanima me je li ubica

150
00:14:02.076 --> 00:14:06.622
uklonio koji dio tijela ili ih
na bilo koji način napastvovao.


151
00:14:07.081 --> 00:14:08.415
Ti si bolestan.

152
00:14:08.791 --> 00:14:10.500
Zanima me, jer ako nije,

153
00:14:10.710 --> 00:14:13.545
onda je lik bezveze.

154
00:14:13.755 --> 00:14:15.714
Kako si tako bezosjećajan?

155
00:14:15.924 --> 00:14:17.674
A ti si majka Tereza?

156
00:14:17.884 --> 00:14:19.676
Ti si rekla Rodu da crkne.

157
00:14:19.886 --> 00:14:22.304
Hiniš da ti je svejedno.

158
00:14:22.513 --> 00:14:25.807
Ovo je stvarnost,
a ne Deathquake.


159
00:14:26.059 --> 00:14:27.059
Jebi se.

160
00:14:27.602 --> 00:14:30.187
Ben pokušava biti faca

161
00:14:30.277 --> 00:14:31.933
i pravi se da se ne boji.

162
00:14:32.023 --> 00:14:34.191
Zdravo, Cindy Freud!

163
00:14:34.400 --> 00:14:36.151
A ko je za tebe faca?

164
00:14:36.361 --> 00:14:39.279
Onaj ko je poševio sve
maturante po abecedi?


165
00:14:39.489 --> 00:14:42.616
Ako sam potrošena,
zašto mi se upucavaš?


166
00:14:42.825 --> 00:14:44.701
Volim iskusne!

167
00:14:44.911 --> 00:14:46.954
Sad je dosta?!
Prestanite!


168
00:14:47.163 --> 00:14:49.164
Svi! Zaboga!

169
00:14:49.749 --> 00:14:51.667
Šta je vama?

170
00:14:53.378 --> 00:14:54.670
Jody...

171
00:14:55.171 --> 00:14:59.007
Na tebe mogu računati
da ćeš reći nešto pametno.


172
00:15:02.220 --> 00:15:03.261
Tata?

173
00:15:04.013 --> 00:15:06.932
Izvinite na smetnji,
g. Marliston,


174
00:15:07.141 --> 00:15:09.351
ali šerif
bi se obratio razredu.


175
00:15:09.441 --> 00:15:10.769
Zdravo, šerife...

176
00:15:10.979 --> 00:15:12.938
Leonard Marliston.
Drago mi je.


177
00:15:13.147 --> 00:15:13.981
I meni.

178
00:15:15.024 --> 00:15:17.609
Učenici,
pomno slušajte šerifa.


179
00:15:19.445 --> 00:15:22.614
Dvoje vaših kolega,
Rod Harper i Stacy Twelfmann,


180
00:15:22.824 --> 00:15:27.619
sinoć su hladnokrvno
ubijeni kod vodopada.


181
00:15:29.247 --> 00:15:32.666
Molim vas da kao prijatelji
i savjesni građani


182
00:15:32.875 --> 00:15:34.793
priđete meni ili mom osoblju

183
00:15:35.003 --> 00:15:37.796
s bilo kakvim informacijama
o ovom užasnom zločinu.


184
00:15:38.548 --> 00:15:40.465
Je li ko osumnjičen?

185
00:15:40.675 --> 00:15:41.383
Nije.

186
00:15:41.592 --> 00:15:43.593
Možete li nam još šta reći?

187
00:15:43.803 --> 00:15:46.263
Ne smijem ništa više reći
o slučaju.


188
00:15:48.516 --> 00:15:53.103
Platon kaže da je polis zdrav
ako je istina dostupna svima.


189
00:15:55.314 --> 00:15:59.860
Platon može otkriti šta želi
kad on bude šerif.


190
00:16:03.156 --> 00:16:05.032
Namjerno to čini.

191
00:16:05.950 --> 00:16:07.367
Naravno.

192
00:16:07.952 --> 00:16:10.287
Zato ga moraš zanemariti.

193
00:16:10.872 --> 00:16:12.748
Misliš da ona ide do kraja?

194
00:16:17.920 --> 00:16:19.004
Sumnjam.

195
00:16:20.006 --> 00:16:21.706
Ko bi htio nju poševiti?

196
00:16:24.594 --> 00:16:25.802
Pogledaj.

197
00:16:42.779 --> 00:16:44.112
Sranje.

198
00:16:44.572 --> 00:16:45.947
Prestani se bacati!

199
00:16:52.163 --> 00:16:54.956
Ja odustajem od veza...

200
00:16:55.166 --> 00:16:58.043
Ali za tebe ima nade.
Dođi. Hajde.


201
00:16:58.252 --> 00:17:00.795
Neću, Jody.
- Dođi. Tužno i patetično.


202
00:17:00.885 --> 00:17:03.588
Svaki dan ga gledaš kako
jede, a nikad ne razgovarate.


203
00:17:03.678 --> 00:17:06.635
Moji su u braku 25 godina,
pa samo gledaju TV.


204
00:17:06.725 --> 00:17:08.381
Idemo tamo.
Razgovarat ćete.


205
00:17:08.471 --> 00:17:09.513
Ne pravi scenu!

206
00:17:17.814 --> 00:17:19.314
Kako ste?

207
00:17:22.610 --> 00:17:25.112
Danas je grozan dan.

208
00:17:25.321 --> 00:17:26.738
Valjda.

209
00:17:38.376 --> 00:17:40.001
Lažove odvratni!

210
00:17:41.379 --> 00:17:42.921
Ubit ću te!

211
00:17:43.881 --> 00:17:45.710
Bolje i to
nego lažov koji puši!


212
00:17:45.800 --> 00:17:47.425
Ubit ću te, govno jedno!

213
00:17:50.638 --> 00:17:52.305
Šta se ovdje dogada?

214
00:17:56.686 --> 00:17:59.312
Kad ti tip kaže da dobro
pušiš, to je kompliment.


215
00:18:01.566 --> 00:18:03.358
Imaš nešto na usnama.

216
00:18:04.277 --> 00:18:07.070
Govori laži o meni!
- To ćeš mi reći u uredu!


217
00:18:08.577 --> 00:18:10.282
Koji ti je
broj telefona, Annette?


218
00:18:11.742 --> 00:18:13.243
Nisam ja.

219
00:18:15.830 --> 00:18:16.997
Šta je ovo bilo?

220
00:18:17.206 --> 00:18:19.583
Dylan je svima rekao
da mu je Annette popušila.


221
00:18:20.585 --> 00:18:22.544
Je li?
- Šališ se?


222
00:18:22.753 --> 00:18:24.004
Ne.

223
00:18:24.213 --> 00:18:26.756
Ona misli da je felacija
Shakespeareov lik.


224
00:18:26.846 --> 00:18:29.896
Ne bi prepoznala kurac
ni da se spotakne na njega.


225
00:18:31.970 --> 00:18:33.513
Baš smiješno.

226
00:18:34.015 --> 00:18:36.433
Šta ti misliš, Mark?

227
00:18:38.603 --> 00:18:41.021
Mislim da su rebarca super.

228
00:19:03.336 --> 00:19:05.420
Kasnimo.

229
00:19:07.131 --> 00:19:08.548
Zdravo, ljepoto.

230
00:19:27.443 --> 00:19:29.945
Dođi, ljepotice.

231
00:19:30.321 --> 00:19:31.821
Drago mi je!

232
00:19:37.954 --> 00:19:38.828
Ko je?

233
00:19:39.914 --> 00:19:41.414
Zdravo, Annette.

234
00:19:42.959 --> 00:19:44.626
Ja sam Loralee Sherman.

235
00:19:44.961 --> 00:19:46.253
Molim?

236
00:19:46.462 --> 00:19:47.963
Loralee Sherman.

237
00:19:48.547 --> 00:19:50.131
Je li ti mama kući?

238
00:19:52.551 --> 00:19:53.677
Nije.

239
00:19:53.886 --> 00:19:56.012
Nije ti rekla da ću doći?

240
00:19:56.430 --> 00:19:57.305
Nije.

241
00:19:57.723 --> 00:20:01.226
Valjda sam zakasnila.
Mogu li ostaviti poruku?


242
00:20:10.278 --> 00:20:12.237
Dobro, samo malo.

243
00:20:16.325 --> 00:20:18.493
Proturite je kroz vrata.

244
00:20:37.263 --> 00:20:39.055
Spreman sam za trke.

245
00:20:40.308 --> 00:20:42.559
Gdje žuriš, ljepotice?

246
00:20:43.477 --> 00:20:46.021
Lakše malo. Uspori.

247
00:20:53.073 --> 00:20:54.946
Ko je ostavio vrata
otvorena? - Ne znam.


248
00:20:55.036 --> 00:20:56.990
Annette?
- Annette?


249
00:20:58.242 --> 00:20:59.075
Annette!

250
00:20:59.702 --> 00:21:00.814
Annette!

251
00:21:09.503 --> 00:21:10.754
Zgrabi ovdje.

252
00:21:10.963 --> 00:21:12.547
I ispod.
Stisni čvrsto.


253
00:21:12.757 --> 00:21:16.343
Zakorači. Težina i
zamah će učiniti svoje.


254
00:21:17.067 --> 00:21:18.887
Najvažnije je
da dobro uhvatiš.


255
00:21:18.977 --> 00:21:20.377
Zgrabi kao pitbul.

256
00:21:21.599 --> 00:21:23.141
Nabavi mi sprej

257
00:21:23.351 --> 00:21:25.435
ili električni pištolj.

258
00:21:25.644 --> 00:21:27.604
Ne. To je protivzakonito.
Dođi.


259
00:21:32.568 --> 00:21:34.444
Pauza.

260
00:21:36.155 --> 00:21:37.447
Marken.

261
00:21:48.918 --> 00:21:51.169
Ovo izgleda kao repriza.

262
00:21:53.589 --> 00:21:56.589
Agent Bronhill. Ovo je
specijalni agent Majestik.


263
00:21:57.050 --> 00:21:59.928
Ko je prvi stigao?
- Moja zamjenica.


264
00:22:01.347 --> 00:22:03.306
Došla sam na
očev poziv u 23 h,


265
00:22:03.516 --> 00:22:05.725
i odmah pozvala šerifa.

266
00:22:08.771 --> 00:22:10.188
Mi ćemo preuzeti.

267
00:22:19.031 --> 00:22:21.157
Sad smo u prvoj ligi.

268
00:22:26.747 --> 00:22:31.584
Na lijevom bedru
urezana je riječ "nevina".


269
00:22:32.211 --> 00:22:34.087
Kao i na prethodne
dvije žrtve.


270
00:22:34.922 --> 00:22:36.548
Kao i Stacy Twelfmann...

271
00:22:36.757 --> 00:22:39.467
U trenutku smrti je
Annette DeWolde bila nevina.


272
00:22:40.553 --> 00:22:44.222
Himen je netaknut. Nema
tragova sperme na odjeći,


273
00:22:44.432 --> 00:22:47.767
koži, kosi,
ustima ni anusu.


274
00:22:49.019 --> 00:22:52.021
Nema ogrebotina ni udaraca
oko spolovila.


275
00:22:52.440 --> 00:22:55.567
Nema nikakvih
dokaza penetracije.


276
00:22:56.819 --> 00:23:00.488
Ni momak kod prvog
napada nije silovan.


277
00:23:01.532 --> 00:23:04.492
Ne mogu vam reći
je li umro nevin,


278
00:23:05.202 --> 00:23:09.247
ali sigurno nije imao
odnos u vrijeme ubistva.


279
00:23:10.624 --> 00:23:14.377
Čini se
da je vaš ubica tačan


280
00:23:14.587 --> 00:23:17.255
u primjeni svog potpisa.

281
00:23:27.266 --> 00:23:28.308
Uđi.

282
00:23:33.147 --> 00:23:34.397
Zdravo, dušo.

283
00:23:35.191 --> 00:23:36.399
Zdravo, tata.

284
00:23:37.067 --> 00:23:38.443
Slušaj...

285
00:23:38.944 --> 00:23:41.446
Moram te pitati
nešto intimno.


286
00:23:41.655 --> 00:23:42.947
O čemu?

287
00:23:43.908 --> 00:23:45.617
O tebi i Kennyju.

288
00:23:46.619 --> 00:23:49.829
Šta, tata?
- Koliko daleko ste otišli?


289
00:23:51.790 --> 00:23:52.874
Otišli?

290
00:23:53.792 --> 00:23:54.959
Znaš...

291
00:23:56.378 --> 00:23:57.712
Dokle ste stigli?

292
00:23:58.881 --> 00:24:00.798
Ljubite li se?

293
00:24:01.884 --> 00:24:03.009
Naravno.

294
00:24:05.346 --> 00:24:08.389
Nisam dijete.
To je normalno.


295
00:24:08.599 --> 00:24:10.099
Nisam prigovarao.

296
00:24:10.809 --> 00:24:12.227
Znam...

297
00:24:13.646 --> 00:24:15.647
Jeste li otišli dalje?

298
00:24:18.734 --> 00:24:23.112
Ne bih te pitao
da nije nužno.


299
00:24:25.616 --> 00:24:29.744
Možete li ići dalje...
nego što jeste?


300
00:24:31.247 --> 00:24:32.372
Da.

301
00:24:36.126 --> 00:24:38.878
Ali ne moraš
brinuti o tome.


302
00:24:41.632 --> 00:24:43.883
Prekinuli smo.

303
00:24:49.473 --> 00:24:52.517
Jesi li razočaran? Tata?

304
00:24:54.895 --> 00:24:57.355
Jesi li razočaran
što sam još nevina?


305
00:24:58.065 --> 00:25:01.192
Ne. Ne, nimalo.

306
00:25:07.032 --> 00:25:09.826
Veoma se ponosim tobom.

307
00:25:14.623 --> 00:25:16.541
Još si moja djevojčica.

308
00:25:21.255 --> 00:25:22.338
Laku noć.

309
00:25:22.548 --> 00:25:23.756
Volim te.

310
00:25:34.935 --> 00:25:37.604
Roditelji moraju znati
šta se događa.


311
00:25:38.188 --> 00:25:40.481
Moramo im reći
kako bira žrtve?


312
00:25:40.691 --> 00:25:42.275
Valjda.

313
00:25:42.693 --> 00:25:44.193
Pravila nalažu suprotno.

314
00:25:44.653 --> 00:25:47.488
Teško je provjeriti priznanje.

315
00:25:47.698 --> 00:25:51.117
A i potičemo imitatore.
- Ovo je nešto drugo.


316
00:25:51.577 --> 00:25:54.329
Ovo nije potpis ubice
nego poruka.


317
00:25:54.872 --> 00:25:55.830
Poruka?

318
00:25:58.542 --> 00:26:00.627
Sazovi hitan sastanak.

319
00:26:00.836 --> 00:26:02.920
Večeras u šest.

320
00:26:03.130 --> 00:26:07.133
Moraju doći roditelji
svih tinejdžera. Hajde.


321
00:26:09.178 --> 00:26:11.512
Nemamo tako veliku dvoranu.

322
00:26:11.972 --> 00:26:14.015
U sportskoj dvorani škole.

323
00:26:14.808 --> 00:26:17.268
Bez djece.
Zasad.


324
00:26:20.064 --> 00:26:22.565
Tu ste, g. Marliston.

325
00:26:22.775 --> 00:26:25.401
O, Jody.... Zdravo.

326
00:26:26.654 --> 00:26:29.989
Završila sam referat
o T.S. Eliotu.


327
00:26:30.324 --> 00:26:31.991
Izvrsno.

328
00:26:33.827 --> 00:26:36.454
Mnogo mi se sviđa.

329
00:26:36.664 --> 00:26:37.705
Dobro.

330
00:26:40.959 --> 00:26:45.213
"Naši usahli glasovi
Kad šapćemo među sobom


331
00:26:46.423 --> 00:26:49.842
Tihi su i besmisleni
Kao vjetar u suhoj travi


332
00:26:50.844 --> 00:26:55.264
Il' pacovi po razbijenu staklu
U našem suhom podrumu."


333
00:27:04.775 --> 00:27:09.737
Mislite li da je zaista
tako među ljudima?


334
00:27:10.406 --> 00:27:12.740
Sve usahlo...

335
00:27:12.908 --> 00:27:16.077
I besmisleno
i beznadežno prazno?


336
00:27:20.207 --> 00:27:22.125
Čuo sam da si prekinula
s Kennyjem.


337
00:27:22.918 --> 00:27:27.130
Kakve to ima veze?
Preboljela sam ga.


338
00:27:28.549 --> 00:27:30.508
Mislite da svaka moja
ozbiljna misao


339
00:27:30.718 --> 00:27:33.761
proizlazi iz jedne
protraćene zime s njim?


340
00:27:34.054 --> 00:27:36.764
Ne, izvini. Ja...

341
00:27:41.603 --> 00:27:46.107
Izvinite. Strašno mi je
neugodno što sam vikala na vas.


342
00:27:46.358 --> 00:27:49.277
Izvinjavam se.
To se mene ne tiče.


343
00:27:56.869 --> 00:27:58.119
Šta je?

344
00:27:58.996 --> 00:28:01.956
Čudno. Vidjela sam nekoga
na vratima.


345
00:28:05.327 --> 00:28:07.026
Jody, nemoj... Jody...
- Šta?


346
00:28:39.036 --> 00:28:40.036
Izađi!

347
00:29:13.403 --> 00:29:15.863
Ima li koga?
- Nema.


348
00:29:16.490 --> 00:29:18.658
Mislim da smo dobro
isprepadali jedno drugo.


349
00:29:21.662 --> 00:29:24.247
Hajde. Moram na sastanak
koji je sazvao tvoj otac.


350
00:29:32.381 --> 00:29:34.090
Možeš li sama?

351
00:29:34.466 --> 00:29:36.551
Hej, g. Marliston?

352
00:29:38.387 --> 00:29:40.346
Možemo li
opet razgovarati?


353
00:29:40.556 --> 00:29:43.432
Naravno.
- Ali samo nas dvoje.


354
00:29:45.978 --> 00:29:47.311
Da.

355
00:29:50.148 --> 00:29:51.607
Naravno...

356
00:29:51.817 --> 00:29:53.317
Idi kući, Jody.

357
00:29:53.527 --> 00:29:54.902
Trči!

358
00:29:58.282 --> 00:30:01.701
Ne smiješ reći roditeljima
da neko ubija djevice.


359
00:30:02.536 --> 00:30:04.662
Možda bi danas
Annette bila živa


360
00:30:04.872 --> 00:30:07.206
da sam otkrio detalj
o prva dva ubistva.


361
00:30:07.416 --> 00:30:10.042
Saberi se.
Moraš biti odgovoran.


362
00:30:10.252 --> 00:30:11.752
Ne diraj me!

363
00:30:12.546 --> 00:30:14.380
I ne govori o odgovornosti!

364
00:30:14.590 --> 00:30:16.757
Znamo šta znači
izbjeći odgovornost.


365
00:30:17.384 --> 00:30:20.094
Ako klinci čuju da neko

366
00:30:21.013 --> 00:30:23.639
ubija djevice,
uslijedit će prokleti...


367
00:30:25.434 --> 00:30:27.059
Festival jebanja.

368
00:30:27.149 --> 00:30:29.749
Bolje i to nego
gomila mrtvih tinejdžera.


369
00:30:48.290 --> 00:30:50.791
Šta ti radiš ovdje?
- A ti?


370
00:30:50.881 --> 00:30:52.788
Skupljam vijesti.
- Izvoli.


371
00:30:52.878 --> 00:30:55.421
Hvala vam što ste došli.

372
00:30:56.632 --> 00:30:58.466
Kao što znate...

373
00:30:59.384 --> 00:31:02.428
U dva dana
izgubili smo troje djece.


374
00:31:03.305 --> 00:31:05.932
Ustanovili smo vezu
između ubistava.


375
00:31:06.224 --> 00:31:07.350
Koju?

376
00:31:08.226 --> 00:31:10.603
Sve tri žrtve su pohađale
ovu srednju školu...


377
00:31:11.813 --> 00:31:15.229
I sve su,
koliko nam je poznato,


378
00:31:15.901 --> 00:31:18.111
bile nevine.

379
00:31:20.447 --> 00:31:24.033
Sveti himen,
ubijaju djevice?!


380
00:31:24.123 --> 00:31:26.202
Kažete da to
nije slučajnost?


381
00:31:26.292 --> 00:31:28.329
Hoćete li nekoga
uskoro uhapsiti?


382
00:31:28.830 --> 00:31:29.616
Ne.

383
00:31:29.706 --> 00:31:31.374
Šta da kažemo djeci?

384
00:31:31.464 --> 00:31:33.709
Poševite se da preživite?

385
00:31:34.252 --> 00:31:35.789
Nisam to rekao.

386
00:31:35.879 --> 00:31:37.588
Ne mogu zaključati kćer.

387
00:31:38.006 --> 00:31:39.674
Ja na tvom mjestu
ne bih brinuo.


388
00:31:39.764 --> 00:31:41.926
Šta želiš reći?

389
00:31:42.135 --> 00:31:43.755
Samo sam se šalio.

390
00:31:43.845 --> 00:31:46.055
Baš si pogodio vrijeme!

391
00:31:46.598 --> 00:31:47.890
Odbij!

392
00:31:52.479 --> 00:31:54.271
Izvrsno!
Pogledaj ih.


393
00:31:54.361 --> 00:31:56.407
Pretvaraju se
u čopor vukova!


394
00:31:56.497 --> 00:31:57.608
Jody, skloni se.

395
00:32:01.822 --> 00:32:04.115
Baterija!
Posudi mi mobilni.


396
00:32:04.324 --> 00:32:06.409
Molim te.
- Nikad ga ne vratiš.


397
00:32:07.160 --> 00:32:09.453
Sjetite se zašto smo ovdje!

398
00:32:10.372 --> 00:32:12.415
Daj mi to.
- Evo.


399
00:32:15.627 --> 00:32:17.795
Zaustavite štampu!
Imam priču.


400
00:32:18.005 --> 00:32:20.131
Ubica djevica terorizira...
Prekidaš.


401
00:32:20.340 --> 00:32:22.383
Ne, nego ubija djevice!

402
00:32:22.592 --> 00:32:23.968
Moram iz hodnika.

403
00:32:24.386 --> 00:32:26.470
Posljednji put vas molim!

404
00:32:28.015 --> 00:32:29.807
Dosta!

405
00:32:31.476 --> 00:32:32.685
O, tata...

406
00:32:36.773 --> 00:32:37.857
Timmy?

407
00:32:40.485 --> 00:32:41.402
Timmy!

408
00:32:41.611 --> 00:32:43.154
Vrati mi mobilni!

409
00:32:46.908 --> 00:32:47.950
Timmy!

410
00:32:49.619 --> 00:32:50.619
Timmy?

411
00:32:54.958 --> 00:32:56.083
Sranje!

412
00:33:01.757 --> 00:33:02.715
Timmy!

413
00:33:07.596 --> 00:33:08.721
Timmy!

414
00:33:14.102 --> 00:33:15.102
Timmy...

415
00:33:32.788 --> 00:33:33.788
Timmy?

416
00:33:44.633 --> 00:33:48.052
Timmy, daj!
Ovo više nije zabavno!


417
00:33:49.971 --> 00:33:53.891
Bit ću ti najbolja
prijateljica. Naj-najbolja.


418
00:34:17.415 --> 00:34:19.250
Je li to za mene?

419
00:34:24.012 --> 00:34:26.424
<b>NEVIN</b>

420
00:35:41.458 --> 00:35:42.583
Nevina.

421
00:36:43.478 --> 00:36:44.895
Gonila me je!

422
00:36:45.105 --> 00:36:47.147
Ubila je Timmyja!
Unutra je!


423
00:36:47.357 --> 00:36:49.775
Držite je!
- Tata, pazi!


424
00:37:22.142 --> 00:37:24.852
Možda je nos bio malo manji.

425
00:37:26.855 --> 00:37:29.565
Imala je sivi pramen ovdje.

426
00:37:32.027 --> 00:37:33.277
Tako, da.

427
00:37:38.783 --> 00:37:39.992
To je ona.

428
00:37:41.661 --> 00:37:43.871
Barem ono što sam vidjela.

429
00:37:45.790 --> 00:37:47.124
Poznajete li je?

430
00:37:47.542 --> 00:37:48.751
Ne znam.

431
00:37:51.046 --> 00:37:53.964
Slušajte me! Slušajte me!

432
00:37:54.174 --> 00:37:56.133
Slušajte me!
- Daj mi zvonce.


433
00:37:56.343 --> 00:37:58.010
Uhvatite me, glupi kreteni!

434
00:37:58.427 --> 00:38:00.637
Zašto ne dođete po mene?!
- Pazi na jezik!


435
00:38:00.727 --> 00:38:01.889
Bila si dobra.

436
00:38:02.098 --> 00:38:04.350
Slušajte, ja sam ih pobio.

437
00:38:04.559 --> 00:38:06.185
Moram telefonirati.

438
00:38:07.187 --> 00:38:08.812
Mama će doći za minutu.

439
00:38:09.022 --> 00:38:10.522
Sve će biti uredu.

440
00:38:13.401 --> 00:38:15.903
Pobio sam tu djecu.
- Pazi na jezik.


441
00:38:16.196 --> 00:38:19.239
Vi ste obični kreteni.

442
00:38:19.449 --> 00:38:22.409
I znate šta? Uživao sam dok
sam ih ubijao. Bili su zli.


443
00:38:22.619 --> 00:38:25.829
Znate šta sam uradio
prije nego što sam ih ubio?


444
00:38:26.581 --> 00:38:27.831
Poljubio sam ih.

445
00:38:28.041 --> 00:38:29.083
Ovako!

446
00:38:32.379 --> 00:38:34.463
Rolly, to mi je ime!
Ne diraj me!


447
00:38:34.881 --> 00:38:37.383
Kad vam kažem!
Znam svoja prava!


448
00:38:54.776 --> 00:38:55.692
Brente.

449
00:38:56.945 --> 00:38:58.654
Sjajan sastanak sinoć.

450
00:38:59.531 --> 00:39:01.407
Uspio si utješiti roditelje.

451
00:39:01.825 --> 00:39:03.409
<i>Jesi li sam?</i>

452
00:39:03.659 --> 00:39:04.571
Jesam.

453
00:39:04.661 --> 00:39:06.656
<i>Dobro. Imam nešto
da ti pokažem.</i>


454
00:39:06.746 --> 00:39:07.997
<i>Šaljem ti faksom.</i>

455
00:39:31.938 --> 00:39:35.065
<i>Gledaš?
Reci da to nije ona.</i>


456
00:39:36.109 --> 00:39:37.103
Ko?

457
00:39:37.193 --> 00:39:40.070
<i>Loralee Sherman.
Reci da to nije ona.</i>


458
00:39:41.573 --> 00:39:44.199
Daj, Brente.
Skroz si poludio.


459
00:39:44.575 --> 00:39:47.953
<i>Htio sam je kontaktirati. Saznao
sam da živi u Zapadnoj Virginiji.</i>


460
00:39:48.288 --> 00:39:50.741
<i>Dva sata odavde.
Idem tamo.</i>


461
00:39:50.831 --> 00:39:52.001
Slušaj, Brente...

462
00:39:52.091 --> 00:39:54.412
Niko je nije čuo ni vidio
već 25 godina.


463
00:39:54.502 --> 00:39:56.247
Zašto bi se pojavila sada

464
00:39:56.337 --> 00:39:58.505
<i>kao manijakalni ubica?</i>

465
00:40:02.343 --> 00:40:04.386
<i>Nazvat ću te poslije.</i>

466
00:40:05.805 --> 00:40:07.973
Šta radiš?
- Šta je?


467
00:40:08.683 --> 00:40:10.976
Prisluškuješ me?
Šta si čula?


468
00:40:11.769 --> 00:40:14.771
Ništa. Podigla sam slušalicu
da nazovem mamu.


469
00:40:15.356 --> 00:40:18.609
Nisam znala kako dobiti
